# Common Admin Tasks

Day-to-day CLI operations for the **{{ org.name }}** organization.

> All commands use `--oid {{ org.oid }}`. Set as a variable for convenience:
> ```bash
> export LC_OID="{{ org.oid }}"
> ```

---

## Sensor Management

```bash
# List all sensors with status
limacharlie sensor list --oid $LC_OID \
  --filter "[].{hostname:hostname,sid:sid,online:is_online,isolated:is_isolated}" --output yaml

# Get details for a specific sensor
limacharlie sensor get --sid <SID> --oid $LC_OID --output yaml

# Isolate a sensor (network containment)
limacharlie sensor isolate --sid <SID> --oid $LC_OID

# De-isolate a sensor
limacharlie sensor rejoin --sid <SID> --oid $LC_OID

# Add a tag
limacharlie tag add --sid <SID> --tag <tag> --oid $LC_OID

# Remove a tag
limacharlie tag remove --sid <SID> --tag <tag> --oid $LC_OID
```

See [Sensor Deployment](https://docs.limacharlie.io/2-sensors-deployment/) and [Endpoint Commands](https://docs.limacharlie.io/8-reference/endpoint-commands/).

