## AI Agent Management

```bash
# List all agents
limacharlie hive list --hive-name ai_agent --oid $LC_OID --output yaml

# Get agent definition
limacharlie hive get --hive-name ai_agent --key <agent-key> --oid $LC_OID --output yaml

# View AI sessions
limacharlie ai sessions list --oid $LC_OID --output yaml

# Rotate Anthropic API key (zero-downtime)
limacharlie secret set --key anthropic-key --value "<NEW-KEY>" --oid $LC_OID
```

