## Case Management

```bash
# List recent cases
limacharlie case list --oid $LC_OID --output yaml

# Get case details
limacharlie case get --id <case_number> --oid $LC_OID --output yaml

# Add a note to a case
limacharlie case add-note --id <case_number> --content "Note text" --type analysis --oid $LC_OID

# Update case status
limacharlie case update --id <case_number> --status acknowledged --oid $LC_OID

# Export case with data
limacharlie case export --id <case_number> --with-data ./case-export --oid $LC_OID
```

See [ext-cases](https://docs.limacharlie.io/5-integrations/extensions/limacharlie/cases/).

