## Troubleshooting Quick Reference

| Symptom | Check | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| Agent not firing | Is the trigger D&R rule enabled? | Enable the rule |
| Agent fires but fails | Is the Anthropic API key valid? | Rotate `anthropic-key` secret |
| Agent fires but no LC API access | Is the agent's LC API key valid? | Check/rotate the agent's secret |
| No detections on a sensor | Is the sensor online? | Check sensor status |
| Sensor offline | Is the VM running? | Check cloud console |
| Rule not matching | Is the rule enabled? | Check `enabled` field |
| FP rule too broad | Review FP rule pattern | Delete with `limacharlie dr fp delete` |
